---
---

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
  <!-- 1 -->
  <div class="card p-5 group">
    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-accent group-hover:bg-accent group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h4 class="font-bold text-ink mb-1.5">Odborné prehliadky VTZ</h4>
    <p class="text-ink-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Vykonávanie odborných prehliadok vyhradených technických zariadení tlakových a plynových, kontroly elektrických spotrebičov.</p>
  </div>
  <!-- 2 -->
  <div class="card p-5 group">
    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-brand group-hover:bg-brand group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h4 class="font-bold text-ink mb-1.5">Školenia obslúh</h4>
    <p class="text-ink-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Obsluhy VTZ tlakových, plynových a zdvíhacích zariadení, revízni technici, bezpečnostní technici.</p>
  </div>
  <!-- 3 -->
  <div class="card p-5 group">
    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-accent group-hover:bg-accent group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h4 class="font-bold text-ink mb-1.5">Spracovanie dokumentácie</h4>
    <p class="text-ink-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Miestne prevádzkové predpisy, chýbajúca dokumentácia, duplikáty pre VTZ tlakové a plynové.</p>
  </div>
  <!-- 4 -->
  <div class="card p-5 group">
    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-brand group-hover:bg-brand group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1010 10c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2h-3.5c-.8 0-1.5-.7-1.5-1.5v-5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2h-1z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h4 class="font-bold text-ink mb-1.5">Kontrola kotlov a vykurovania</h4>
    <p class="text-ink-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Pravidelná a rozšírená kontrola kotlov a vykurovacích systémov podľa platnej legislatívy.</p>
  </div>
  <!-- 5 -->
  <div class="card p-5 group">
    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-accent group-hover:bg-accent group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M16 7V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h4 class="font-bold text-ink mb-1.5">BOZP a ochrana zdravia</h4>
    <p class="text-ink-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Výkon technika BOZP, technika požiarnej ochrany, výchova a vzdelávanie zamestnancov.</p>
  </div>
  <!-- 6 -->
  <div class="card p-5 group">
    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-brand group-hover:bg-brand group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h4 class="font-bold text-ink mb-1.5">Pracovná zdravotná služba</h4>
    <p class="text-ink-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Výkon PZS pre kategórie 1 a 2, spracovanie dokumentácie, sprostredkovateľské služby.</p>
  </div>
</div>
